Map for CS:Source

cs_ASSAULT_NP - Hostage Rescue

Counter-Terrorists: Terrorists have taken
over the Nothern Petrol Warehouse. They have 
taken some of the workers hostage. You must
rescue them!!

Terrorists: Prevent the CTs from
rescuing the hostages. 

Other Notes: There are 2 hostage rescue zones.
